[{"id": 403, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-wizard\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Arcane Deflection</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The math was already done before the blow landed.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">When you or an ally takes damage, perform an <strong>Arcana</strong> check. On success, the damage is reduced \u2014 remove 1 <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Die</span> from the hit. The magic crackles visibly.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> The attacker is also <strong>Rattled</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Wizard</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 404, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-wizard\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">React</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Counterspell</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Not a spell. An argument. You win.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">When an enemy uses a magical ability, perform an <strong>Arcana</strong> check. On success, negate the effect \u2014 the ability fizzles and is wasted. No damage or conditions apply.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> The caster is <strong>Rattled</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Wizard</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 405, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-wizard\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Frost Nova</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Everything stops. You choose when.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Arcana</strong> check. On success, blast frost in all directions \u2014 all adjacent enemies are <strong>Rooted</strong> and take 1 cold damage each.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> They are also <strong>Rattled</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Wizard</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 406, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-ranger\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Hunt and Track</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">They left a trail. You are reading it.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Survival</strong> check. On success, follow a creature's trail \u2014 you always know their direction and rough distance until the <strong>Scene</strong> changes significantly.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Also learn how many there are and when they passed.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Ranger</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 407, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-ranger\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Hunter's Mark</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">The hunt starts the moment you see them.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform a <strong>Survival</strong> check. On success, mark a target \u2014 you gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on every <strong>Action</strong> against them until they are removed from the <strong>Scene</strong>. The mark transfers to a new target when they fall.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Target is also <strong>Exposed</strong>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Ranger</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 408, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-ranger\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Condition</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Camouflage</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">While in hand: the terrain becomes you.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">While this card is in hand and you are in natural terrain, you are <strong>Hidden</strong>. Enemies must succeed on a <strong>Perception</strong> check to detect you before targeting you.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> <strong>Hidden</strong> persists through one slow, careful movement.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Ranger</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 409, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-ranger\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Pinning Shot</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Not meant to kill. Meant to stop.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Perform an <strong>Agility</strong> check. On success, loose an arrow that pins a target in place \u2014 they are <strong>Rooted</strong> until they break free with an <strong>Action</strong>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> They are also <strong>Rattled</strong> \u2014 the wound stings.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Ranger</div><div class=\"tier-float\"><span>t1</span></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 410, "HTML": "<div class=\"card fighter acc-fighter\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Weapon Master</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">Your hands know the weight of everything.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Passive</div><div class=\"effect-text\">Whenever you equip any <span class=\"ix ix-item\">Item</span> card into your Equip zone, <strong>Draw</strong> 1.</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"zone-label\">Note</div><div class=\"effect-text\" style=\"font-size:8.5px; color:#5a4a20; font-style:italic;\">Triggers on any equip \u2014 weapon, armor, or otherwise. Rewards active loadout management every <strong>Scene</strong>.</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Fighter</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 411, "HTML": "<div class=\"card fighter acc-fighter\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Battlemaster</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">You've already seen how this ends.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">React</div><div class=\"effect-text\">Spend any of your <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost</span> dice to reduce an attack against an ally, or add to an ally's attack \u2014 if you are within range to intervene fictionally.</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"zone-label\">Cost</div><div class=\"effect-text\" style=\"font-size:8.5px; color:#5a4a20; font-style:italic;\">Draws from your personal <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost</span> dice pool. No <strong>Action</strong> cost. Range is the GM's call.</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Fighter</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 412, "HTML": "<div class=\"card fighter acc-fighter\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Loadout</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">You never go in without a plan.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Standard Deck Recipe</div><div class=\"loadout-recipe\"><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">10 <span class=\"kw kw-fighter\">Fighter</span> Ability Cards</span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">2 other Core <span class=\"kw kw-fighter\">Fighter</span> cards</span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-background\">Background</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-ancestry\">Ancestry</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-bond\">Bond</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-flaw\">Flaw</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">5 <span class=\"kw kw-instinct\">Instincts</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-item\">Item</span> (Tier 1)</span></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Fighter</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 414, "HTML": "<div class=\"card paladin acc-paladin\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Conviction \u00b7 Defiance</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">Faith is the action. Doubt is the cost.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Conviction</div><div class=\"effect-text\">When you play an ability and narrate how it upholds your Oath, <strong>Draw</strong> 1.</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"zone-label\">Defiance</div><div class=\"effect-text\">When Entering a <strong>Scene</strong>, <strong>Discard</strong> your Oath \u2014 explain how you are going against it. <strong>Discard</strong> your hand, <strong>Draw</strong> again, lose half your <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Dice</span>. Oath returns only when drawn naturally.</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Paladin</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 415, "HTML": "<div class=\"card paladin acc-paladin\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Loadout</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">You go in with your word already given.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Standard Deck Recipe</div><div class=\"loadout-recipe\"><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">10 <span class=\"kw kw-paladin\">Paladin</span> Ability Cards</span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">2 other Core <span class=\"kw kw-paladin\">Paladin</span> cards</span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-background\">Background</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-ancestry\">Ancestry</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-bond\">Bond</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-flaw\">Flaw</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">5 <span class=\"kw kw-instinct\">Instincts</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-item\">Item</span> (Tier 1)</span></div></div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"zone-label\">Special Setup</div><div class=\"effect-text\" style=\"font-size:8.5px; color:#5a4a20; font-style:italic;\">Your Oath card begins play in your Active area. It is GM-awarded and earned through play \u2014 start with one provided by your GM.</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Paladin</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 416, "HTML": "<div class=\"card ranger acc-ranger\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Trapper</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">The best ambush is one they walk into.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Setup</div><div class=\"effect-text\">Stow up to 2 Trap cards face-down per <strong>Scene</strong>. <strong>Draw</strong> 1 for each trap prepared.</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"zone-label\">Trigger</div><div class=\"effect-text\">When a trap's trigger condition is met, reveal the card to interrupt the triggering effect before it resolves.</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Ranger</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 417, "HTML": "<div class=\"card ranger acc-ranger\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Discipline</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">Patience is the sharpest edge.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Any Check \u2014 Before Result</div><div class=\"effect-text\">Remove any number of <span class=\"kw kw-crit\">Crit</span> dice from the roll and gain them as <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost</span> dice instead. All removed dice take effect on the Check before conversion.</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"effect-text\" style=\"font-size:8.5px; color:#3a5a3a; font-style:italic;\">Reactions fall outside this scope. Discipline applies to any Check the <span class=\"ix ix-ranger\">Ranger</span> initiates or participates in.</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Ranger</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 418, "HTML": "<div class=\"card ranger acc-ranger\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Loadout</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">Everything in its place before you move.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Standard Deck Recipe</div><div class=\"loadout-recipe\"><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">10 <span class=\"kw kw-ranger\">Ranger</span> Ability Cards</span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">2 other Core <span class=\"kw kw-ranger\">Ranger</span> cards</span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-background\">Background</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-ancestry\">Ancestry</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-bond\">Bond</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-flaw\">Flaw</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">5 <span class=\"kw kw-instinct\">Instincts</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-item\">Item</span> (Tier 1)</span></div></div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"zone-label\">Special Setup</div><div class=\"effect-text\" style=\"font-size:8.5px; color:#3a5a3a; font-style:italic;\">Trap cards are drawn from a separate Trap pool \u2014 not from your Class Cards. Choose 3 Trap cards at character creation.</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Ranger</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 419, "HTML": "<div class=\"card cleric acc-cleric\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Prayer</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">You don't ask for power. You ask for purpose.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Each <strong>Scene</strong> \u2014 Declare Aloud</div><div class=\"effect-text\"><em>[Verb] the [Noun]</em> \u2014 your petition for this <strong>Scene</strong>. All <span class=\"kw kw-crit\">Crit</span> dice from any roll bank here (up to your Level).</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"zone-label\">Once Per <strong>Scene</strong></div><div class=\"effect-text\">Spend ALL banked dice as <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost</span> on one <strong>Action</strong> that serves your prayer. Flip this card face-down. Refreshes next <strong>Scene</strong>.</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Cleric</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 420, "HTML": "<div class=\"card cleric acc-cleric\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Absolution</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">The wound heals. What caused it can too.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Passive</div><div class=\"effect-text\">Whenever you heal an ally, they may immediately <strong>Discard</strong> 1 Bane or Status card from their hand.</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"effect-text\" style=\"font-size:8.5px; color:#5a5a7a; font-style:italic;\">The ally chooses whether to <strong>Discard</strong>. Healing is defined as any card that restores <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Dice</span> or removes damage.</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Cleric</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 421, "HTML": "<div class=\"card cleric acc-cleric\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Loadout</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">You arrive in service of something larger.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Standard Deck Recipe</div><div class=\"loadout-recipe\"><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">10 <span class=\"kw kw-cleric\">Cleric</span> Ability Cards</span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">2 other Core <span class=\"kw kw-cleric\">Cleric</span> cards</span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-background\">Background</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-ancestry\">Ancestry</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-bond\">Bond</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-flaw\">Flaw</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">5 <span class=\"kw kw-instinct\">Instincts</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-item\">Item</span> (Tier 1)</span></div></div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"effect-text\" style=\"font-size:8.5px; color:#5a5a7a; font-style:italic;\">No special setup. Prayer card begins face-up in Active area, ready to receive your first petition.</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Cleric</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 422, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bard acc-bard\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Showstopper</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">You make everyone else look good. Or you take the stage.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Once Per <strong>Scene</strong> \u2014 <strong>Discard</strong> 1</div><div class=\"effect-text\">Choose one:</div><div class=\"choose-list\"><div class=\"choose-item\"><strong>Mimic</strong> \u2014 copy an ally's <strong>Action</strong> as they perform it. You roll independently.</div><div class=\"choose-item\"><strong>Lead</strong> \u2014 an ally copies your <strong>Action</strong> as you perform it. They roll independently.</div></div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"effect-text\" style=\"font-size:8px; color:#5a3a7a; font-style:italic;\">Flip this card face-down when used. Refreshes next <strong>Scene</strong>.</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Bard</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 423, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bard acc-bard\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Improvise</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">The best performance is the one nobody expected.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Once Per <strong>Scene</strong></div><div class=\"effect-text\">Play any playable card from your hand as a <span class=\"ix ix-react\">React</span> \u2014 narrate a performance reason for it. No <strong>Action</strong> cost. Play it at printed cost.</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"effect-text\" style=\"font-size:8px; color:#5a3a7a; font-style:italic;\">Eligible cards: anything playable. Banes and Statuses are held, not played \u2014 they do not qualify. Flip face-down when used. Refreshes next <strong>Scene</strong>.</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Bard</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 424, "HTML": "<div class=\"card bard acc-bard\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Loadout</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">You travel light. You arrive loud.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Standard Deck Recipe</div><div class=\"loadout-recipe\"><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">10 <span class=\"kw kw-bard\">Bard</span> Ability Cards</span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">2 other Core <span class=\"kw kw-bard\">Bard</span> cards</span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-background\">Background</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-ancestry\">Ancestry</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-bond\">Bond</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-flaw\">Flaw</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">5 <span class=\"kw kw-instinct\">Instincts</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-item\">Item</span> (Tier 1)</span></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Bard</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 425, "HTML": "<div class=\"card warlock acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Pact</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">Power has a price. You agreed to the terms.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Before or After Any Check</div><div class=\"effect-text\">Spend a <span class=\"kw kw-hd\">Hit Die</span> from your pool \u2014 reroll it fresh and add the new result to the check. That die is removed from your pool. On a 6, it returns.</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"zone-label\">Patron Cost</div><div class=\"effect-text\">First invocation this <strong>Scene</strong>: choose which <strong>Mark</strong> you owe. Each invocation after the first: the GM rolls your next <strong>Mark</strong>.</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 426, "HTML": "<div class=\"card warlock acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Infernal Patron</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">A being that deals in cost \u2014 everything given has a price, and the ledger is always open.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\" style=\"gap:3px;padding:5px 10px;\"><div class=\"zone-label\" style=\"font-size:6px;letter-spacing:0.8px;margin-top:0;\">The Marks of</div><div class=\"marks-row\" style=\"gap:2px;\"><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"mark-num infernal-num\">1</span><span class=\"mark-word infernal-word\" style=\"font-size:7.5px;padding:1px 4px;\">Hunger</span></div><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"mark-num infernal-num\">2</span><span class=\"mark-word infernal-word\" style=\"font-size:7.5px;padding:1px 4px;\">Iron</span></div><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"mark-num infernal-num\">3</span><span class=\"mark-word infernal-word\" style=\"font-size:7.5px;padding:1px 4px;\">Ruin</span></div><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"mark-num infernal-num\">4</span><span class=\"mark-word infernal-word\" style=\"font-size:7.5px;padding:1px 4px;\">Judgement</span></div><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"mark-num infernal-num\">5</span><span class=\"mark-word infernal-word\" style=\"font-size:7.5px;padding:1px 4px;\">Ash</span></div><div class=\"mark-pill\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">6</span><strong>\u2605 Choose</strong></div></div><div class=\"zone-label\" style=\"font-size:6px;letter-spacing:0.8px;margin-top:0;\">Invoke Their Name</div><div class=\"effect-text\" style=\"font-size:9px;line-height:1.4;\">Call them forth and select one of the <strong>Marks</strong> above to warp the <strong>Scene</strong> in your favor. Then <strong>Shuffle</strong> this card into your <strong>Draw</strong> Pile.</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div style=\"background:rgba(138,32,16,0.08);border:0.5px solid rgba(138,32,16,0.3);border-radius:3px;padding:3px 5px;\"><div class=\"bane-label\" style=\"font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:6px;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#8a2010;margin-bottom:1px;\">\ud83d\udd12 Bane \u2014 To Clear This:</div><div class=\"effect-text\" style=\"font-size:7.5px;line-height:1.4;color:#8a2010;font-style:italic;\">Announce that your Patron has arrived. Roll a d6 to determine which <strong>Mark</strong> you must pay. The GM decides the cost before this <strong>Scene</strong> ends.</div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 427, "HTML": "<div class=\"card warlock acc-warlock\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Loadout</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">You didn't choose this. You agreed to it.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Standard Deck Recipe</div><div class=\"loadout-recipe\"><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">10 <span class=\"kw kw-warlock\">Warlock</span> Ability Cards</span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">2 other Core <span class=\"kw kw-warlock\">Warlock</span> cards</span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-background\">Background</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-ancestry\">Ancestry</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-bond\">Bond</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-flaw\">Flaw</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">5 <span class=\"kw kw-instinct\">Instincts</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-item\">Item</span> (Tier 1)</span></div></div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"zone-label\">Special Setup</div><div class=\"effect-text\" style=\"font-size:8.5px; color:#6a1a30; font-style:italic;\">Choose 1 Patron card at character creation. It begins play in your Active area. The Patron card is also shuffled into your deck as a Bane after each use.</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Warlock</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 428, "HTML": "<div class=\"card druid acc-druid\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Beastform</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">You don't wear another shape. You remember it.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Equip System</div><div class=\"effect-text\">You have 3 Beastform cards chosen at creation. Equipping one unequips all others \u2192 <strong>Draw</strong> 1. Swap freely between <strong>Scenes</strong>.</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"zone-label\">While Equipped</div><div class=\"effect-text\">The Kinship passive on your active Beastform is always true. Transform freely \u2014 make a Check to use a Full Form ability.</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Druid</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 429, "HTML": "<div class=\"card druid acc-druid\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Grove</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">Failure is not waste. It is what you tend.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Session Start</div><div class=\"effect-text\">Search your deck for 1 ability card. Place it in the Grove with 1 d6. <strong>Shuffle</strong>.</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"zone-label\">During Play</div><div class=\"effect-text\">When any player fails a Check on an ability card, take it into your Grove with 1 d6. Capacity: Tier cards.</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"zone-label\">Each <strong>Scene</strong> Start</div><div class=\"effect-text\">Add 1 d6 to every card in the Grove. Return any card to its owner with all accumulated d6s as <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost</span> dice.</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Druid</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 430, "HTML": "<div class=\"card druid acc-druid\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Loadout</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">You carry only what grows with you.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Standard Deck Recipe</div><div class=\"loadout-recipe\"><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">10 <span class=\"kw kw-druid\">Druid</span> Ability Cards</span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">2 other Core <span class=\"kw kw-druid\">Druid</span> cards</span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-background\">Background</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-ancestry\">Ancestry</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-bond\">Bond</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-flaw\">Flaw</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">5 <span class=\"kw kw-instinct\">Instincts</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-item\">Item</span> (Tier 1)</span></div></div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"zone-label\">Special Setup</div><div class=\"effect-text\" style=\"font-size:8.5px; color:#3a5a1a; font-style:italic;\">Choose 3 Beastform cards at creation from the Beastform pool: Wolf \u00b7 Spider \u00b7 Raven \u00b7 Serpent \u00b7 Toad. They do not count as Class Cards.</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Druid</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 431, "HTML": "<div class=\"card barbarian acc-barbarian\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Rage</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">Everything that hurts you makes you worse to face.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Fuel \u2014 Rage Pool</div><div class=\"effect-text\">When you fail a Check, place those rolled dice in your Rage pool. When you take damage, place the damage dice from each hit into your Rage pool.</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"zone-label\">Frenzy \u2014 5+ Dice</div><div class=\"effect-text\">Immediately top-deck and play the top card of your deck \u2014 narrate how your rage shapes it. That <strong>Action</strong> gains <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 3</span>. Unplayable cards generate 1 <span class=\"kw kw-resolve\">Resolve</span>. Rage pool fully clears.</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"zone-label\">Spend \u2014 Retribution</div><div class=\"effect-text\">At any point, spend your entire pool for Retribution (see Card 2).</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Barbarian</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 432, "HTML": "<div class=\"card barbarian acc-barbarian\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Retribution</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">They shouldn't have touched them.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">React \u2014 When Ally Suffers</div><div class=\"effect-text\">Spend your entire Rage pool. Roll all those dice. Keep the highest (Tier \u00d7 2) results and add them to your next Check targeting the source.</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"zone-label\">After Retribution</div><div class=\"effect-text\">Rage pool resets to zero. Works in any <strong>Scene</strong> \u2014 <strong>Combat</strong>, social, exploration. The GM interprets what \"targeting the source\" means.</div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"effect-text\" style=\"font-size:8px; color:#6a1a0a; font-style:italic;\">Tier 1: keep highest 2 \u00b7 Tier 2: keep highest 4 \u00b7 Tier 3: keep highest 6</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Barbarian</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 433, "HTML": "<div class=\"card barbarian acc-barbarian\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Loadout</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">You don't prepare. You endure.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Standard Deck Recipe</div><div class=\"loadout-recipe\"><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">10 <span class=\"kw kw-barbarian\">Barbarian</span> Ability Cards</span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">2 other Core <span class=\"kw kw-barbarian\">Barbarian</span> cards</span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-background\">Background</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-ancestry\">Ancestry</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-bond\">Bond</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-flaw\">Flaw</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">5 <span class=\"kw kw-instinct\">Instincts</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-item\">Item</span> (Tier 1)</span></div></div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"effect-text\" style=\"font-size:8.5px; color:#6a1a0a; font-style:italic;\">No special setup. Place your Rage pool area \u2014 a clear space for d6 dice \u2014 beside your player board.</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Barbarian</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 434, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-rogue\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Ability</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Ace</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"flv\">Always one more card up the sleeve.</div><div class=\"hr\"></div><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">Once per <strong>Scene</strong>: when you play a card and succeed on the check, gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on your next check this beat. This triggers automatically \u2014 no action required.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\"><span class=\"kw kw-crit\">1</span> Draw a card instead of gaining <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span>.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Rogue</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 436, "HTML": "<div class=\"card rogue acc-rogue\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Core</span><span></span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Loadout</div><div class=\"hdr-sub\">Two decks. One plan. Neither visible.</div></div><div class=\"card-body\"><div class=\"zone-label\">Standard Deck Recipe</div><div class=\"loadout-recipe\"><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">10 <span class=\"kw kw-rogue\">Rogue</span> Ability Cards</span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">2 other Core <span class=\"kw kw-rogue\">Rogue</span> cards</span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-background\">Background</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-ancestry\">Ancestry</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-bond\">Bond</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-flaw\">Flaw</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">5 <span class=\"kw kw-instinct\">Instincts</span></span></div><div class=\"recipe-row\"><span class=\"recipe-dot\">\u00b7</span><span class=\"recipe-text\">1 <span class=\"kw kw-item\">Item</span> (Tier 1)</span></div></div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"zone-label\">Special Setup</div><div class=\"effect-text\" style=\"font-size:8.5px; color:#4a3a7a; font-style:italic;\">Your <span class=\"ix ix-rogue\">Rogue</span> Ability Cards are kept as a separate Ability Deck \u2014 never shuffled with the rest. Each <strong>Scene</strong>, <strong>Draw</strong> up to 3 from it alongside your normal hand.</div></div><div class=\"idtag\">Rogue</div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 449, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-instinct\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Instinct</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Bold</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">True to your character, perform any <strong>Action</strong> in a Bold manner. If the GM agrees it is Bold, Gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 2</span> on the <strong>Action</strong>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\">For each <span class=\"kw kw-crit\">Crit</span>, the result is one tier more Bold than you expected.</div></div></div><div class=\"sp\"></div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 450, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-instinct\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Instinct</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Perceptive</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">True to your character, perform any <strong>Action</strong> in a Perceptive manner. If the GM agrees it is Perceptive, Gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 2</span> on the <strong>Action</strong>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\">For each <span class=\"kw kw-crit\">Crit</span>, the result is one tier more Perceptive than you expected.</div></div></div><div class=\"sp\"></div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}, {"id": 451, "HTML": "<div class=\"card acc-instinct\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Instinct</span><span class=\"cap cap-neutral\">Act</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Tenacious</div></div><div class=\"cbody\"><div class=\"elbl\">Effect</div><div class=\"etxt\">True to your character, perform any <strong>Action</strong> in a Tenacious manner. If the GM agrees it is Tenacious, Gain <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 2</span> on the <strong>Action</strong>.</div><div class=\"csec\"><div class=\"clbl\">Crit</div><div class=\"crow\"><div class=\"ci\">For each <span class=\"kw kw-crit\">Crit</span>, the result is one tier more Tenacious than you expected.</div></div></div><div class=\"sp\"></div></div></div>", "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-24"}]